longBusinessSummary: Coor Service Management Holding AB provides facility management services in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, and Finland. The company offers workplace services, including reception, post, and freight handling services; property services, including property maintenance and security solutions; and energy optimization. It also provides integrated facility management, cleaning, and food and beverage services. Coor Service Management Holding AB was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Solna, Sweden.
